{"tid":2229691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普確診︱試未經評審療法成最矚目「白老鼠」 港大專家料下周康復樂觀","createTime":"2020-10-04T14:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T15:14:31.000Z","uid":41861,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1fb64262702bf237810736ef13822eff35623f1","tid":2229691,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普感染武漢肺炎，據報他在染疫後短時間內，同時接受瑞德西韋（Remdesivir）及美國生物技術公司Regeneron開發的抗體雞尾酒（antibody cocktail）治療。港大醫學院微生物學系臨床助理教授薛達表示，該款抗體雞尾酒的臨床數據尚未經同儕評審（peer review），特朗普成為了該藥最矚目、非常重要的「白老鼠」；但他傾向相信，接受治療「多好過少」，預料特朗普下周康復機會樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n薛達指出，抗體雞尾酒是結合兩種或以上抗體，對抗單一病毒的療法，即使病毒基因突變，抗體黏附及中和病毒的機會也較高。Regeneron曾研發針對中東呼吸綜合症的抗體，有效減低死亡率。至於武肺抗體雞尾酒成效，該公司9月29日也發放新聞稿，闡述在小型臨床實驗裡，高劑量藥物能減低病毒量，也能快速改善染病症狀，惟公司沒有披露詳細數據，實驗成果亦未經同儕評審。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，抗體雞尾酒確實療效仍然存疑，急需大型的人體臨床試驗證實，而它與瑞德西韋結合治療能發揮多大作用，也難以說準，換言之，染疫後短時間便用上述藥物的特朗普，就是最囑目、非常重要的「白老鼠」（ a very important guinea pig）。<br />\n<br />\n惟薜達稱，對付RNA病毒的基本原則是盡快多管齊下治療，故可以理解擁有全球最好醫療照顧的特朗普，願意接受新嘗試。他相信，特朗普下周康復機會樂觀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/6FASS6KERRB2PBBWX2IGNYFP5A/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3DsKSQ1d4GMkRcC8AZvmN37b5swDXqMYJmpm9aKbg3pAZSNJ1kn_oUa4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2F6FASS6KERRB2PBBWX2IGNYFP5A%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3DsKSQ1d4GMkRcC8AZvmN37b5swDXqMYJmpm9aKbg3pAZSNJ1kn_oUa4k&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=29c8c13f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2F6FASS6KERRB2PBBWX2IGNYFP5A%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3DsKSQ1d4GMkRcC8AZvmN37b5swDXqMYJmpm9aKbg3pAZSNJ1kn_oUa4k&h=0b5c7062\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/6FASS6KERRB2PBBWX2IGNYFP5A/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3DsKSQ1d4GMkRcC8AZvmN37b5swDXqMYJmpm9aKbg3pAZSNJ1kn_oUa4k</a>"},{"pid":"978f48582d4df1aab2f1bb02871b66976cc1fd73","tid":2229691,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045a4d1d7bd8b36d7be54ac4c5958a02115e9835","tid":2229691,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"黑暗兵法，無徵不信<br />\n試藥成功，豔陽高照"},{"pid":"b0299de05ad261aef91ac6bcbd0a952ea2f8845c","tid":2229691,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc2bcc20f1dcde038cbc1b9999b1b7665fe30af4","tid":2229691,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"呢啲療法係唔係好貴？  有冇機會太規模採用"},{"pid":"56496c2f7deb65d44f6ef929e4fb2a55b3dce275","tid":2229691,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"果然搵官試藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}